### Summary 
We are requesting to mint 17500000 GEO to be minted on the ODIN chain for the cosmos Ecosystem airdrop.

### Details
50% of the total GEO supply will be minted on the ODIN chain in the next few months.
GEO, the first ODT token, will be distributed among the following:

1. ODIN Stakers &  liquidity providers ($ODIN/Osmos)
2. Atom Stakers
3. Osmosis Stakers

Minimum amount & snapshot dates to be announced.

Thank you!
